Gitanaalthough you might not see her often, gitana is a founding member of the dom’s coffee family. earlier on in the business’s history, she worked the front of house as a barista, but her talents have been needed elsewhere for the last couple of years. without gitana, there would be no dom’s coffee!Andriusif the first person you think of when you hear someone say “dom’s coffee” is andrius, we wouldn’t be surprised. there are few people in this world who are more outgoing and willing to make new friends than andrius! a perpetual problem-solver, there’s no doubt that he’s a major reason why dom’s coffee has had the success we’ve enjoyed!Astayou might mistake her for a ray of sunshine, but really its just her beautiful blonde hair. asta is the personality that helps keep dom’s coffee operating in such an optimistic and enjoyable atmosphere. if you stop by doms cheese shop, asta is also a walking encyclopedia of information about your favorite cultured dairy products!
